NOTE ON DERIVED MODELS
================================================================================

The LoRA adapters published on HuggingFace Hub from this repository are derived
works of the base models. Their use is also subject to the licenses of those
base models:

  - openai/whisper-large-v3:        Apache License 2.0
  - Qwen/Qwen2-Audio-7B-Instruct:   Apache License 2.0 (with separate Qwen Terms)

The training datasets are used under their respective licenses:

  - atlasia/MoulSot-Full:    See the dataset card on HuggingFace.
  - UBC-NLP/Casablanca:      See the dataset card on HuggingFace.

Users of the fine-tuned adapters are responsible for respecting all upstream
licenses.
